Delivery Accumulation Scanner

See accumulation before the move

Our tool highlights stocks showing heavy delivery-based buying without significant price expansion. These patterns often appear before base formation and trend reversals.

We identify NSE stocks showing abnormal volume and high delivery activity without price expansion a common signature of accumulation. The output helps traders focus on stocks worth deeper chart analysis.

How to Read Results

Showing stocks with high delivery and volume participation while price remains relatively stable (Potential Accumulation Phase).

Score Formula: (Delivery% × 1) + (VolumeSpike × 10)
Higher score indicates stronger participation relative to recent averages.
⚠️ Important: This is NOT investment advice or buy/sell recommendation. High delivery & volume does not guarantee future price movement.
